Package edu.umn.cs.csci3081w.project.model

Class StorageFacility

java.lang.Object
edu.umn.cs.csci3081w.project.model.StorageFacility
public class StorageFacility extends Object
Represents a storage facility for buses and trains. The StorageFacility manages the inventory of small and large buses, as well as electric and diesel trains.
